00:40:17.772 --> 00:40:21.212
jump to KRAS, the selection towards BRF,

694
00:40:21.772 --> 00:40:21.852
it

695
00:40:22.752 --> 00:40:23.912
almost disappears. So

696
00:40:25.412 --> 00:40:26.752
that means that KRAS has a

697
00:40:27.632 --> 00:40:31.252
very strong antagonistic effect against BRF, and

698
00:40:31.612 --> 00:40:34.292
the same is true the other way around, but not so much.

699
00:40:34.352 --> 00:40:35.952
So whenever you jump to BRF,

700
00:40:36.812 --> 00:40:39.672
the KRAS selection, it also

