00:40:48.632 --> 00:40:52.252
reason why you don't see that often would be because of this path.

705
00:40:52.672 --> 00:40:53.562
Getting KRAS has a

706
00:40:54.812 --> 00:40:56.592
large antagonistic effect against BRF.

707
00:40:57.392 --> 00:41:01.092
And you actually see that APC and KRAS, they don't influence

