00:41:20.412 --> 00:41:22.252
are both happening very often, that you

714
00:41:23.352 --> 00:41:26.932
see them co-occurring, and not so much because they

715
00:41:27.032 --> 00:41:29.052
actually help each other.

716
00:41:30.532 --> 00:41:31.712
Okay. So

717
00:41:32.612 --> 00:41:36.302
besides that, I want you to see that you can also

718
00:41:36.432 --> 00:41:40.132
start to formalize and actually do statistical

719
00:41:40.172 --> 00:41:41.292
tests

720
00:41:42.972 --> 00:41:46.952
just because you have actual coefficients, and then you can compare, so

721
00:41:47.172 --> 00:41:47.992
you can just

